<section class="lp-section lp-geef lp-reveal in" id="geef" style="padding: 120px 0">
    <div class="lp-container">
        <div class="lp-geef-head">
            <div>
                <p class="lp-eyebrow">The Principle</p>
                <h2 class="lp-h2">
                    Four phases. <em>One loop</em>. <br />
                    The work, refined until it holds.
                </h2>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="lp-lede">
                    GEEF is the pipeline that powers every run in the Atelier.
                    A briefing is grounded in real sources, executed into a draft,
                    evaluated by a crew of reviewers — and rewritten,
                    again and again, <em style="color: var(--hero); font-style: italic">until it converges</em>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="geef-flow">
            <div class="ribbon"><span class="ink"></span></div>
            <div class="loop">
                <LandingIllustrations Name="IterationLoop" />
                <div class="loop-label">↻ &nbsp;until convergence</div>
            </div>

            <div class="geef-phase">
                <div class="num">
                    <span class="ord">Phase G</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ico"><LandingIllustrations Name="PhaseGrounding" /></div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="name" style="margin: 0">Grounding</h3>
                    <p class="copy" style="padding: 0; margin: 14px 0">
                        Gathers the facts — <em>web research, your knowledge base, documents, papers</em> — and filters out the noise before the draft begins.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="pip-row">
                    <span class="pip"></span>
                    <span>Sources gathered</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="geef-phase">
                <div class="num">
                    <span class="ord">Phase E</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ico"><LandingIllustrations Name="PhaseExecution" /></div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="name" style="margin: 0">Execution</h3>
                    <p class="copy" style="padding: 0; margin: 14px 0">
                        An <em>executor</em> model writes the first full draft from the briefing and the gathered context.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="pip-row">
                    <span class="pip"></span>
                    <span>First draft written</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="geef-phase">
                <div class="num">
                    <span class="ord">Phase E</span>
                    <span class="iter-badge">Iter <b>×3</b></span>
                </div>
                <div class="ico"><LandingIllustrations Name="PhaseEvaluation" /></div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="name" style="margin: 0">Evaluation</h3>
                    <p class="copy" style="padding: 0; margin: 14px 0">
                        A <em>crew of reviewers</em> critiques the draft — flagging errors, weak arguments, unclear passages, each with severity.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="pip-row">
                    <span class="pip"></span>
                    <span>Findings · severity · revision</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="geef-phase">
                <div class="num">
                    <span class="ord">Phase F</span>
                </div>
                <div class="ico"><LandingIllustrations Name="PhaseFinalize" /></div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="name" style="margin: 0">Finalize</h3>
                    <p class="copy" style="padding: 0; margin: 14px 0">
                        The converged text is polished and exported — <em>PDF, Word, Markdown</em>, or sent onward to your workflow.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="pip-row">
                    <span class="pip"></span>
                    <span>Sealed · exported</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 28px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 16px">
            <span class="lp-mono-caption">Every transition is logged. Every iteration auditable.</span>
            <span class="lp-mono-caption" style="color: var(--ink-2)">G &nbsp;→&nbsp; E &nbsp;↻&nbsp; E &nbsp;→&nbsp; F</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
